\/24\/kull-maruf-sadaqah-smiling\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Every good deed is charity, even smiling","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery good deed is charity. Verily, it is a good deed to meet your brother with a smiling face, and to pour what is left from your bucket into your brother's vessel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14334,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/fulfill-trust-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Fulfilling trusts honestly an act of charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe honest Muslim storekeeper, who carries out his orders completely, giving with a cheerful heart and paying those whom he was ordered to pay, he is one of two who have given charity.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1371, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32125,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/cheerful-face-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Cheerful face, guiding travelers are charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSmiling in the face of your brother is your charity. Enjoining good and forbidding evil is charity. Guiding a lost man through the land is your charity. Lending your eyesight to a man who cannot see\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":885,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/06\/24\/kull-maruf-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Every good deed rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery good deed is charity.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1005 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0651 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0641\u064d \u0635\u064e\u062f\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0629\u064c 1005 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0645\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0643\u0627\u0629 \u0628\u0627\u0628 \u0628\u064a\u0627\u0646 \u0623\u0646 \u0627\u0633\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062f\u0642\u0629 \u064a\u0642\u0639 \u0639\u0644\u0649 \u0643\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5444,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/20\/prophet-always-smiling\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Smiling: The Prophet would always smile at Jarir","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, never avoided me ever since I embraced Islam. I would never see him but with a smile on his face. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2475 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Muslim \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":45,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/26\/virtue-visiting-sick\/","url_meta":{"origin":882,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Virtue of visiting the sick for Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 26, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever visits a sick person will remain in an orchard of Paradise until he returns.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u00a02568 Grade: Sahih (authentic) a